summary: IMMEDIATELY FOLLOWING HEAVY RAIN STORMS, MY 2005 SUBARU LEGACY WAGON HAD PROBLEMS STARTING AND RUNNING. THE HOLE CAR SHACKS REALLY BAD.  I KNOW TWO OTHER PEOPLE WITH THE SAME PROBLEM. MY DEALER SAID MANY PEOPLE HAVE COME IN WITH A 2005 WITH THAT SAME PROBLEM.  IT STARTED AT 18K AND STILL HAVEN'T BEEN ABOUT TO FIX AFTER 80K. THE ENGINE 'STUTTERS' OR 'MISFIRES'. I CANT GET MY CHECK ENGINE LIGHT TO COME OFF.  *TR
